-- ECB Workers’ Pensions not Protected Against Inflation, FAS Says
-- B y   A l e x   W e b b
-- 2012-04-15T12:59:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-15/ecb-workers-pensions-not-protected-against-inflation-fas-says.html
European Central Bank employees’
pensions are not protected against inflation, the Frankfurter
Allgemeine Sonntagszeitung  reported , citing Carlos Bowles, an
employee spokesman.  “We don’t understand why the ECB leadership refuses to
protect our pensions against inflation,” the newspaper quoted
Bowles as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
